<item>
            <title>[FELIX-4515] BundleRevision for system extension has no capabilities</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-4515</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The BundleRevision for a system extension bundle has currently no capabilities. I think it should at least have the identity capability.&lt;br/&gt;
Currently BundleRevisionImpl explicitely sets the capabilites to an empty list for an extensions.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
